Package therian.operator.copy

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BeanCopier
    Copies Object to Object.
    BeanToMapCopier
    Copy a bean's properties into a Map.
    ContainerCopier<TARGET>
    Tries to convert source and target to Iterables, copy source elements onto corresponding target elements, then to add remaining elements to target.
    ContainerCopier.Dynamic<TARGET>  
    ContainerCopier.ToArray  
    ContainerCopier.ToEnumeration  
    ContainerCopier.ToIterable  
    ContainerCopier.ToIterator  
    ConvertingCopier
    Copy Operator that attempts overwriting conversion for writable target positions storing immutable values.
    Copier<SOURCE,TARGET>
    Copy Operator superclass.
    ElementCopier
    Tries to copy between arrays/iterables using Element positions.
    MapCopier
    Copies between maps, handling supported conversions between keys/values.
    MapToBeanCopier
    Copy a Map's properties onto a bean.
    PropertyCopier<SOURCE,TARGET>
    Copies based on annotations.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    PropertyCopier.NullBehavior
    Describes the PropertyCopier's behavior when presented with a null source value.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    PropertyCopier.Mapping
    Configures a PropertyCopier subclass for property mapping, using a fluent syntax of "mapping: value from foo to bar, value from x to y, etc.".
    PropertyCopier.Mapping.Value
    Specifies mapping for a property value.
    PropertyCopier.Matching
    Configures a PropertyCopier subclass for property matching.
